<h1>Office of Investigations (OI)</h1>

<div class="r">
<a class="clean" href="/about-oig/about-us/leadership/cantrell.pdf"><img src="./images/oi-cantrell.jpg" width="208" alt="Gary Cantrell - Deputy Inspector General for Investigations" />
